1
00:00:39,020 --> 00:00:40,360
May I be like the stars

2
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:41,580
and you like the moon.

3
00:00:42,450 --> 00:00:43,670
As long as the world remains,

4
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:45,780
so shall we.

5
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:03,830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

6
00:01:04,430 --> 00:01:06,060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

7
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,370
I want to be with you forever.

8
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:14,920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

9
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,480
You and she are ultimately different.

10
00:01:37,970 --> 00:01:39,600
Have you ever

11
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:41,789
truly cared for me?

12
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,250
No.

13
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:46,360
Never.

14
00:01:54,650 --> 00:01:57,720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

15
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:03,310
May we live and die together,

16
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,040
and share life and death as one.

17
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:45,790
[Moonlight Mystique]

18
00:02:46,410 --> 00:02:50,000
[Episode 39]

19
00:02:55,020 --> 00:02:57,250
The former Lady Fu Ling was spirited and resolute,

20
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,730
with swift and ruthless judgment.

21
00:02:58,750 --> 00:02:59,750
Although you are holding a sharp blade,

22
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,660
there’s no opportunity to wield it.

23
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,340
What a pity.

24
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,840
Why don't I give you a chance?

25
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:07,510
What do you want?

26
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:14,750
I've said that

27
00:03:14,990 --> 00:03:17,680
once I've returned, I shall reign supreme over the world.

28
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:20,420
Although the Eastern Continent's Eternals and demons are weak,

29
00:03:20,450 --> 00:03:22,230
a good number of them collectively

30
00:03:23,090 --> 00:03:25,329
makes for a decent supplement.

31
00:03:25,380 --> 00:03:27,060
As long as you obey

32
00:03:27,100 --> 00:03:29,260
and capture Eternals and demons for me,

33
00:03:29,290 --> 00:03:31,040
you are allowed to enter and exit

34
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:33,500
Cold Spring Palace freely.

35
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:38,940
After all,

36
00:03:38,970 --> 00:03:40,650
you used to do this sort of thing all the time,

37
00:03:40,670 --> 00:03:41,620
didn’t you?

38
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:48,190
No way.

39
00:03:52,850 --> 00:03:55,280
What if Chong Zhao's life is at stake?

40
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:57,260
Let's see how you choose.

41
00:04:06,860 --> 00:04:07,850
Chong Zhao!

42
00:04:08,650 --> 00:04:09,700
Xi.

43
00:04:13,010 --> 00:04:13,900
Xi.

44
00:04:14,510 --> 00:04:15,480
Chong Zhao.

45
00:04:16,570 --> 00:04:17,740
You are still here.

46
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,019
You really are still here.

47
00:04:20,209 --> 00:04:22,190
There’s still so much we haven’t accomplished yet.

48
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,810
I know you're waiting for me.

49
00:04:25,470 --> 00:04:27,110
I won't disappear so easily.

50
00:04:27,130 --> 00:04:28,660
How sincere

51
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,870
and touching.

52
00:04:29,900 --> 00:04:31,230
Actually, the existence of you two

53
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:32,480
is not something

54
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,330
I find entirely unacceptable.

55
00:04:38,570 --> 00:04:39,740
Chong Zhao.

56
00:04:40,050 --> 00:04:41,380
Persuade her well.

57
00:04:41,409 --> 00:04:42,850
Instead of resisting,

58
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,460
why not obey me?

59
00:04:44,490 --> 00:04:46,780
That's the only wise choice.

60
00:04:49,350 --> 00:04:50,350
Xi.

61
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:52,550
You were forced to be a demon for ten years

62
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:53,810
and suffered for ten years.

63
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:55,290
You finally escaped Cold Spring Palace

64
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:56,650
to become Bai Xi again.

65
00:04:56,670 --> 00:04:58,750
You must not go back to your old ways.

66
00:04:58,790 --> 00:05:00,350
The righteousness of the world

67
00:05:00,380 --> 00:05:03,050
and your future is always more important than my life.

68
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:04,320
Don't you ever feel threatened by him.

69
00:05:04,340 --> 00:05:06,370
That's not what I want to hear.

70
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:11,070
Zhao!

71
00:05:12,450 --> 00:05:13,450
Zhao!

72
00:05:14,710 --> 00:05:15,790
Xi.

73
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:17,610
Remember,

74
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:19,610
regardless of how Mo Li treats me,

75
00:05:19,630 --> 00:05:21,480
even if he kills me,

76
00:05:21,610 --> 00:05:24,040
you mustn't give in to him.

77
00:05:30,350 --> 00:05:32,350
How stubborn.

78
00:05:34,010 --> 00:05:36,070
I really don't understand

79
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,990
why you would fall for

80
00:05:38,010 --> 00:05:39,650
such a boring and stubborn person.

81
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:42,100
You will

82
00:05:42,409 --> 00:05:44,420
never understand his loyalty!

83
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:46,000
Your so-called morality

84
00:05:46,020 --> 00:05:48,810
is the most hypocritical and ridiculous in my eyes.

85
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,610
I may have given you a chance,

86
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:54,030
but that doesn't mean you are irreplaceable.

87
00:05:54,050 --> 00:05:55,540
Since you don't appreciate it,

88
00:05:55,570 --> 00:05:57,490
you can just stand by and watch

89
00:05:57,510 --> 00:06:00,390
how the Eternals and demons grovel at my feet,

90
00:06:00,420 --> 00:06:01,900
begging for mercy.

91
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:09,190
Xiu Yan once said

92
00:06:09,220 --> 00:06:10,040
he could feel that

93
00:06:10,060 --> 00:06:12,180
the Xing Yue Divine Bow is right above the Eastern Continent.

94
00:06:12,210 --> 00:06:13,770
But no matter how I summon it,

95
00:06:13,790 --> 00:06:15,640
the Divine Bow wouldn't appear.

96
00:06:15,660 --> 00:06:18,700
The Contemplation Stone and the Outlander King's Sword also had no reaction to it.

97
00:06:18,730 --> 00:06:21,100
The Contemplation Stone and the Sword acknowledged you as its master

98
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,160
because they sensed that

99
00:06:22,190 --> 00:06:23,710
you have Xing Yue's Divine Mantle,

100
00:06:23,740 --> 00:06:25,380
but the Xing Yue Bow remained completely silent.

101
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:26,960
Unless...

102
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:29,290
Unless it's not yet awakened

103
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:30,630
and doesn't know it's a Divine Bow.

104
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:33,640
Back then, the Xing Yue Divine Bow could defy Xing Yue's own wishes

105
00:06:33,659 --> 00:06:34,980
and shot Jing Yuan down.

106
00:06:35,010 --> 00:06:37,250
This means it has its own consciousness.

107
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:38,740
It's different from other divine objects.

108
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:43,490
Bad news.

109
00:06:44,070 --> 00:06:46,020
Mo Li launched a sudden attack on various demon clans and Eternal sects.

110
00:06:46,050 --> 00:06:47,490
Many Eternals and demons have nowhere to go.

111
00:06:47,510 --> 00:06:49,000
They've all fled to the Polar Region for refuge.

112
00:06:49,030 --> 00:06:50,150
Mo Li has gathered several demon warriors

113
00:06:50,170 --> 00:06:51,409
to attack the Polar Region.

114
00:06:54,140 --> 00:06:56,110
The Polar Region's terrain is vast and complex.

115
00:06:56,130 --> 00:06:58,050
It's certainly possible to take in the Eternals and demons seeking refuge.

116
00:06:58,080 --> 00:06:59,600
I believe the demon warriors of Bright Moon Palace

117
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:00,660
are not afraid of a battle.

118
00:07:00,690 --> 00:07:01,800
But here in the Polar Region,

119
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:03,980
there are also many little demons that you saved.

120
00:07:04,010 --> 00:07:05,240
If Mo Li attacks,

121
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:06,670
they won't be able to withstand it.

122
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:08,970
On the day we established this palace in the Polar Region,

123
00:07:08,990 --> 00:07:11,540
I made it clear that no one would be allowed to encroach on my territory.

124
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,630
What are you trying to do?

125
00:07:14,950 --> 00:07:17,110
Jing Yuan left all of his divine power to me.

126
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:19,480
I can summon the Purple Moon above the Polar Region

127
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:21,820
and protect the entire Polar Region with my primal power.

128
00:07:21,910 --> 00:07:23,750
Although the primal power of the Demon Lord is strong,

129
00:07:23,770 --> 00:07:25,900
the Polar Region spans hundreds of thousands of miles of land.

130
00:07:25,930 --> 00:07:27,970
If you form a barrier with your divine power,

131
00:07:27,990 --> 00:07:29,740
it will inevitably consume your power continuously.

132
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,670
Master.

133
00:07:30,690 --> 00:07:32,280
You're draining yourself.

134
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:35,250
Anyone who comes to the Polar Region,

135
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,600
whether an Eternal or a demon,

136
00:07:36,620 --> 00:07:38,500
is entrusting their life to me.

137
00:07:39,140 --> 00:07:40,710
I will protect them all.

138
00:07:41,140 --> 00:07:42,020
Master!

139
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,640
Aren't you going to stop him?

140
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:48,880
If he isn't going to resolve matters this way,

141
00:07:48,900 --> 00:07:51,020
he wouldn’t be the Master of Bright Moon Palace

142
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,820
or the Fan Yue I know.

143
00:07:53,590 --> 00:07:55,250
He has endured too much suffering

144
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,640
and faced too many hardships in the past.

145
00:07:56,659 --> 00:07:58,220
That's why he wants to stand in front of others

146
00:07:58,250 --> 00:07:59,690
and shield those who are also suffering.

147
00:08:00,980 --> 00:08:02,720
This is his choice.

148
00:08:02,900 --> 00:08:05,400
I agree and I won't stop him.

149
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:07,450
As for my choice...

150
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,920
I've already told you,

151
00:08:09,710 --> 00:08:11,480
We shall fight side by side,

152
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:13,060
sharing both life and death.

153
00:09:10,370 --> 00:09:11,410
Purple Moon!

154
00:09:11,430 --> 00:09:13,840
-It's the Purple Moon! 
 -It's the Purple Moon!

155
00:09:14,090 --> 00:09:15,520
It's the Purple Moon! Look!

156
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:18,990
Purple Moon!

157
00:09:25,930 --> 00:09:28,450
It's the Demon Lord who is using the Purple Lunar Power to form a barrier

158
00:09:28,860 --> 00:09:30,820
in order to block Mo Li's attack.

159
00:09:30,850 --> 00:09:33,330
I didn't expect that us Eternals have to escape to the Polar Region

160
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:34,300
and receive protection from Fan Yue

161
00:09:34,330 --> 00:09:35,730
in order to survive.

162
00:09:46,820 --> 00:09:47,670
Fan Yue.

163
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:50,960
I'm fine.

164
00:09:51,370 --> 00:09:53,140
Previously, Eternals and demons all believed that

165
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:55,230
the Master of Bright Moon was ruthless by nature.

166
00:09:55,260 --> 00:09:56,830
Now, they will all know that

167
00:09:56,850 --> 00:09:59,090
you are the most merciful one.

168
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,790
It doesn't matter whether they know or not.

169
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,000
What matters is

170
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:04,870
no matter what happens next,

171
00:10:04,900 --> 00:10:06,900
I mustn't allow Mo Li's wild ambitions succeed.

172
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:08,910
60,000 years ago,

173
00:10:08,940 --> 00:10:10,570
Mo Li destroyed the Divine Region.

174
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,880
60,000 years later,

175
00:10:11,900 --> 00:10:13,750
I won't let him destroy the Eastern Continent again.

176
00:10:18,290 --> 00:10:20,240
It was exactly this Purple Moon that

177
00:10:20,260 --> 00:10:21,870
gave me immense hope back then.

178
00:10:23,340 --> 00:10:25,670
It's the same this time.

179
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:39,410
The appearance of the Purple Moon

180
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,800
will protect the Eternals and demons.

181
00:10:40,820 --> 00:10:41,660
Mo Li,

182
00:10:42,330 --> 00:10:43,870
you can't win after all.

183
00:10:43,890 --> 00:10:46,080
Do you really think that the Purple Moon's protection of the Polar Region

184
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:48,700
will safeguard those Eternals and demons for a lifetime?

185
00:10:48,730 --> 00:10:50,430
No one can stop me

186
00:10:50,460 --> 00:10:52,070
from doing what I want.

187
00:10:52,730 --> 00:10:54,900
Shuo and Fan Yue won't sit back and do nothing.

188
00:10:54,930 --> 00:10:57,080
I'm sure they'll find a way to restrain you.

189
00:10:58,060 --> 00:10:58,990
Really?

190
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:03,230
I'm afraid the Human Race can't wait till then.

191
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:05,350
What do you mean?

192
00:11:05,490 --> 00:11:06,870
The humans are unaware of the Eternals, the demons,

193
00:11:06,910 --> 00:11:08,210
or the Polar Region,

194
00:11:08,290 --> 00:11:10,230
nor do they know about the impending catastrophe in the world.

195
00:11:10,250 --> 00:11:11,630
They're still at the same place,

196
00:11:11,630 --> 00:11:12,890
living their peaceful lives.

197
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:15,400
The Purple Moon can barely safeguard the Polar Region as it is.

198
00:11:15,430 --> 00:11:17,690
How can it protect the entire Human Race?

199
00:11:17,710 --> 00:11:18,820
You're...

200
00:11:19,020 --> 00:11:20,760
You're actually planning to target the Human Race?

201
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:22,310
You're at least an ancient god.

202
00:11:22,330 --> 00:11:23,380
How could you be this despicable?

203
00:11:29,820 --> 00:11:31,060
In my eyes,

204
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:33,350
there is only success or failure.

205
00:11:33,490 --> 00:11:35,340
There's no such thing as benevolence or otherwise.

206
00:11:38,990 --> 00:11:40,030
Tomorrow,

207
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:43,870
I'll put on a good show for you.

208
00:12:39,950 --> 00:12:41,600
Are you satisfied

209
00:12:42,270 --> 00:12:43,980
with this show?

210
00:12:48,980 --> 00:12:50,730
You want to use human blood

211
00:12:50,750 --> 00:12:52,410
to break the Purple Lunar Barrier?

212
00:12:54,340 --> 00:12:55,910
The Purple Moon's divine power is extremely yang,

213
00:12:55,930 --> 00:12:57,670
while human blood is extremely yin.

214
00:12:57,690 --> 00:12:59,120
Yin and yang neutralizes each other,

215
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:01,580
so why not?

216
00:13:07,860 --> 00:13:09,750
Kill me if you dare!

217
00:13:13,330 --> 00:13:15,570
Killing you would be too easy.

218
00:13:15,590 --> 00:13:17,240
It's only fun if I torture you.

219
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:18,860
Offering the blood of thousands

220
00:13:18,880 --> 00:13:20,480
will surely incur heaven's wrath

221
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:22,110
Heaven's wrath?

222
00:13:23,210 --> 00:13:25,510
If the Heaven is capable of killing me,

223
00:13:25,540 --> 00:13:28,300
I would have died 60,000 years ago.

224
00:13:28,770 --> 00:13:30,520
Heaven has set a rule that only a Supreme Deity

225
00:13:30,540 --> 00:13:32,750
can completely kill another Supreme Deity.

226
00:13:32,780 --> 00:13:35,270
Even the Heaven has to follow its own rules.

227
00:13:39,370 --> 00:13:40,280
Sacrifice?

228
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:05,950
Look at the scenery.

229
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:08,630
Blood staining the Polar Region.

230
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:11,490
How spectacular!

231
00:14:29,090 --> 00:14:30,740
You'll face retribution.

232
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:33,240
You'll definitely face retribution!

233
00:14:33,270 --> 00:14:34,250
Shut up!

234
00:14:36,740 --> 00:14:38,530
I think I am already hearing

235
00:14:38,930 --> 00:14:41,900
the blood currents climbing over the Purple Lunar Barrier.

236
00:14:47,490 --> 00:14:48,730
Very soon...

237
00:14:57,460 --> 00:14:58,220
Master.

238
00:14:58,250 --> 00:15:00,340
All the Eternals and demons seeking refuge have been taken care of.

239
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,310
In the face of a powerful enemy,

240
00:15:01,340 --> 00:15:03,310
both sides have set aside their past prejudices

241
00:15:03,330 --> 00:15:04,520
and are living in peace.

242
00:15:09,390 --> 00:15:10,330
Master.

243
00:15:10,470 --> 00:15:11,470
What's wrong?

244
00:15:11,660 --> 00:15:12,870
Are you not feeling well?

245
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:15,230
-Master!
-Fan Yue!

246
00:15:22,420 --> 00:15:23,310
What's going on?

247
00:15:30,280 --> 00:15:31,580
Human blood sacrifice?

248
00:15:32,380 --> 00:15:34,210
The Purple Lunar Barrier has been broken.

249
00:15:46,930 --> 00:15:47,920
Xi!

250
00:15:48,570 --> 00:15:49,770
Shuo, I'm fine.

251
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:56,190
You're finally here.

252
00:15:56,670 --> 00:15:59,180
Chong Zhao would never commit such a heinous act as a human blood sacrifice.

253
00:15:59,210 --> 00:16:00,970
You are nothing like him.

254
00:16:00,990 --> 00:16:02,960
How could a weak and incompetent Chong Zhao

255
00:16:02,990 --> 00:16:04,710
ever compare to me?

256
00:16:06,380 --> 00:16:09,320
The human blood broke the Purple Lunar Barrier so quickly.

257
00:16:09,350 --> 00:16:11,500
It seems that you are no longer Jing Yuan.

258
00:16:11,530 --> 00:16:13,410
Whether I'm Fan Yue or Jing Yuan,

259
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,780
I won't let you succeed.

260
00:16:17,410 --> 00:16:18,880
The indiscriminate killing of

261
00:16:18,900 --> 00:16:20,320
innocent humans is utterly inhumane.

262
00:16:20,350 --> 00:16:21,380
Mo Li.

263
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:23,090
You don't deserve to be a deity.

264
00:16:23,110 --> 00:16:24,990
That's not up to you to decide.

265
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,150
You all...

266
00:16:27,870 --> 00:16:29,950
can't stop me from achieving my grand plan.

267
00:16:49,580 --> 00:16:51,240
You've clearly overestimated your abilities.

268
00:17:08,780 --> 00:17:10,930
You only have Xing Yue's Divine Mantle.

269
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:13,220
Now without the power of the Contemplation Stone,

270
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:14,349
you're nothing but an ant

271
00:17:14,369 --> 00:17:16,119
in my eyes.

272
00:17:46,330 --> 00:17:48,060
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

273
00:17:48,310 --> 00:17:50,530
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

274
00:17:50,590 --> 00:17:52,150
♫My love brought tears♫

275
00:17:52,470 --> 00:17:54,350
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

