549
00:32:24,460 --> 00:32:26,370
I will never comprehend the true meaning of the world.

550
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:28,710
Having met you in this lifetime,

551
00:32:28,840 --> 00:32:30,640
I already have no regrets.

552
00:32:29,570 --> 00:32:35,940
♫All the answers are already explained♫

553
00:32:32,340 --> 00:32:33,750
Chong Zhao.

554
00:32:34,010 --> 00:32:35,700
If there's a next life,

555
00:32:36,360 --> 00:32:39,010
let's live as an ordinary couple,

556
00:32:37,280 --> 00:32:39,560
♫I'll owe you all of my life♫

557
00:32:40,120 --> 00:32:41,320
shall we?

558
00:32:40,330 --> 00:32:43,630
♫But we're destined to part♫

559
00:32:44,300 --> 00:32:50,170
