00:33:00,610 --> 00:33:05,470
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

565
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:08,810
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

566
00:33:09,420 --> 00:33:13,390
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

567
00:33:13,940 --> 00:33:20,890
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

568
00:33:18,020 --> 00:33:19,280
Don't give up.

569
00:33:20,460 --> 00:33:21,990
I have faith in you.

570
00:33:21,690 --> 00:33:24,910
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

571
00:33:22,190 --> 00:33:24,290
You can definitely triumph over Mo Li.

572
00:33:26,300 --> 00:33:28,330
♫When my star falls only for you♫

573
00:33:29,590 --> 00:33:30,600
♫When the heavens fall♫

574
00:33:31,520 --> 00:33:35,960
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

575
00:33:37,060 --> 00:33:39,560
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

576
00:33:40,470 --> 00:33:44,050
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

577
00:33:42,490 --> 00:33:43,620
Xi!

578
00:33:44,260 --> 00:33:45,850
Xi!

579
00:33:45,130 --> 00:33:55,080
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

580
00:34:02,380 --> 00:34:04,560
You keep saying you want to marry Xing Yue,

581
00:34:04,580 --> 00:34:06,420
but that's only because you can't get her

582
00:34:06,440 --> 00:34:08,739
and are trying to claim her through bloodshed.

583
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:11,540
Love in this world can never come from possession.

584
00:34:12,710 --> 00:34:13,860
Love?

585
00:34:15,639 --> 00:34:16,909
I never needed

586
00:34:16,929 --> 00:34:18,570
such a stupid thing.

587
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:21,310
I will prove to all of you that

588
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:23,480
even without love,

589
00:34:23,510 --> 00:34:25,520
I can still have it all.

590
00:34:26,530 --> 00:34:27,880
Xing Yue,

591
00:34:28,639 --> 00:34:31,330
you will be mine.

592
00:34:39,370 --> 00:34:40,810
I finally understand

593
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:42,960
why ten years ago,

594
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:45,190
when that demon tried to swallow me and Xi,

595
00:34:46,110 --> 00:34:48,270
he said that Xi had spiritual energy.

596
00:34:48,199 --> 00:34:55,179
[Unbridled Pavilion]

597
00:34:48,300 --> 00:34:49,790
I also finally understand

598
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:51,880
why Jin Yao couldn't kill her.

599
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:55,360
Xi was never an ordinary human.

600
00:34:55,929 --> 00:34:57,530
She is the Xing Yue Divine Bow.

601
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:00,960
I should have guessed it.

602
00:35:03,390 --> 00:35:05,030
The Xing Yue Divine Bow

603
00:35:05,050 --> 00:35:07,020
was born with deity Xing Yue.

604
00:35:09,180 --> 00:35:10,350
Fan Yue.

605
00:35:10,700 --> 00:35:12,740
Don't you think Heaven is so heartless?

606
00:35:13,280 --> 00:35:15,570
Did they bring Xi into this world

607
00:35:17,150 --> 00:35:20,020
just for her to keep sacrificing herself for me?

608
00:35:20,890 --> 00:35:22,100
In this lifetime,

609
00:35:22,890 --> 00:35:24,850
you are Bai Shuo and she is Bai Xi.

610
00:35:25,410 --> 00:35:26,480
You've already surpassed

611
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:28,060
the relationship between a Supreme Deity and their divine weapon,

612
00:35:28,090 --> 00:35:30,220
and have become each other's closest family in this world.

613
00:35:30,650 --> 00:35:31,570
She saved you

614
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:34,390
not out of her mission as the Divine Bow,

615
00:35:34,660 --> 00:35:36,370
but as a sister protecting her younger sister.

616
00:35:36,920 --> 00:35:38,580
Her biggest wish

617
00:35:38,970 --> 00:35:40,450
was for you to be well.

618
00:35:41,660 --> 00:35:42,780
For her,

619
00:35:44,170 --> 00:35:45,810
you have to pull yourself together.

620
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:51,390
[Unbridled Pavilion]

621
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:48,810
Xi sacrificed her life

622
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:50,360
in exchange for mine.

623
00:35:51,470 --> 00:35:52,870
I will honor her wish

624
00:35:54,010 --> 00:35:55,480
and be invincible.

625
00:35:56,660 --> 00:35:58,640
I will surely get rid of Mo Li,

626
00:35:59,810 --> 00:36:00,730
avenging her

627
00:36:02,700 --> 00:36:04,700
and all those who have died.

628
00:36:09,430 --> 00:36:10,270
Fan Yue!

629
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:11,800
Fan Yue!

630
00:36:11,820 --> 00:36:12,510
Master!

631
00:36:20,070 --> 00:36:21,300
What happened?

632
00:36:22,610 --> 00:36:23,630
Master used the Purple Lunar Power

633
00:36:23,660 --> 00:36:25,070
to protect the entire Polar Region.

634
00:36:25,090 --> 00:36:26,960
It has been consuming his divine power,

635
00:36:26,980 --> 00:36:28,850
but with the addition of Mo Li's mass human blood sacrifice,

636
00:36:29,140 --> 00:36:30,330
I'm afraid...

637
00:36:30,350 --> 00:36:31,440
What will happen?

638
00:36:31,470 --> 00:36:33,800
The Purple Moon is extremely yang, while human blood is extremely yin.

639
00:36:33,820 --> 00:36:35,300
With Mo Li's sinister blood sacrifice,

640
00:36:35,330 --> 00:36:37,520
human blood is now infused into the Purple Moon's divine power,

641
00:36:37,540 --> 00:36:38,750
creating a force of both extreme yin and yang

642
00:36:38,780 --> 00:36:40,400
that is clashing in Master's body.

643
00:36:40,420 --> 00:36:41,590
Even with Master's divine body,

644
00:36:41,590 --> 00:36:43,770
he's unable to bear the strain of these two opposing forces.

645
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:45,260
If this continues,

646
00:36:45,540 --> 00:36:46,910
I'm afraid that Master...

647
00:36:47,290 --> 00:36:49,180
I'm afraid Master's divine vein will snap,

648
00:36:49,260 --> 00:36:51,060
and he will blow up and die.

649
00:36:56,420 --> 00:36:57,610
Stay still!

650
00:36:58,130 --> 00:37:00,300
Mo Li used the Heavenly Divine Miror

651
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:03,360
to absorb the power of Eternals and demons to practice evil techniques.

652
00:37:03,630 --> 00:37:06,490
His Hidden power is stronger than before.

653
00:37:06,830 --> 00:37:08,160
Stop struggling.

654
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:10,230
The power of you Eternals and demons

655
00:37:10,260 --> 00:37:13,170
are no match for an ancient deity's divine power.

656
00:37:27,230 --> 00:37:28,650
Mo Li.

657
00:37:28,830 --> 00:37:30,720
Don't you dare assume we'll yield to you

658
00:37:30,750 --> 00:37:32,420
just because you're stronger.

659
00:37:33,070 --> 00:37:34,320
Whether a nobody like you surrenders to me

660
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:36,100
is of no importance to me.

661
00:37:36,120 --> 00:37:38,350
Either way, I could crush you easily with a flick of my hand.

662
00:37:38,380 --> 00:37:40,380
Why are you gathering all the Eternals and demons together here?

663
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:42,030
What are you trying to do?

664
00:37:42,290 --> 00:37:45,120
I just want to play a game with all of you.

665
00:37:45,450 --> 00:37:46,410
Bai Shuo.

666
00:37:47,060 --> 00:37:48,770
You guys are familiar with her, right?

667
00:37:50,720 --> 00:37:52,750
Now, all of your lives

668
00:37:52,770 --> 00:37:54,160
are in Bai Shuo’s hands.

669
00:37:54,640 --> 00:37:55,610
Whether you live

670
00:37:55,810 --> 00:37:57,110
or die

671
00:37:57,770 --> 00:37:59,870
is completely up to her.

672
00:38:22,990 --> 00:38:27,940
[To the esteemed Lady Tian Huo]

673
00:38:24,040 --> 00:38:27,040
Hidden Lord Mo Li, with the lives of all Eternals and demons at stake,

674
00:38:27,070 --> 00:38:29,760
demands that Bai Shuo goes to Cold Spring Palace alone

675
00:38:29,780 --> 00:38:31,350
within the next day.

676
00:38:31,430 --> 00:38:34,200
If she does not arrive within the next day, or more than one person arrives,

677
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:36,380
he will kill all Eternals and demons.

678
00:38:36,460 --> 00:38:38,500
We urge Lady Tian Huo to think carefully.

679
00:38:39,210 --> 00:38:40,880
I've fed him the pill,

680
00:38:40,900 --> 00:38:41,930
but he's still unconscious.

681
00:38:44,910 --> 00:38:45,730
What's wrong?

682
00:38:46,110 --> 00:38:46,900
Nothing.

683
00:38:48,040 --> 00:38:49,040
Tian Huo.

684
00:38:49,060 --> 00:38:50,720
At this point,

685
00:38:50,750 --> 00:38:52,180
no matter what happens,

686
00:38:52,210 --> 00:38:53,290
don't hide anything from me.

687
00:38:54,660 --> 00:38:56,260
It's a letter from the demon warriors.

688
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:58,120
Mo Li has taken control of all the Eternals and demons

689
00:38:58,150 --> 00:38:59,150
and sent word that

690
00:38:59,740 --> 00:39:01,700
you are to go to Cold Spring Palace alone.

691
00:39:01,720 --> 00:39:03,350
Otherwise, in one day,

692
00:39:03,380 --> 00:39:05,110
he will kill all Eternals and demons.

693
00:39:26,620 --> 00:39:28,860
You were always by my side during

694
00:39:29,680 --> 00:39:31,510
every life-and-death moment in the past.

695
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:33,090
This time,

696
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:35,460
I'll have to face it myself.

697
00:39:36,610 --> 00:39:38,590
Do you remember I once said that

698
00:39:39,020 --> 00:39:40,790
the words "Xing Yue's Divine Mantle"

699
00:39:41,980 --> 00:39:43,420
seems very light?

700
00:39:45,100 --> 00:39:47,930
It seems so light that I could just assume it as a story,

701
00:39:48,290 --> 00:39:49,730
but it also seems so heavy.

702
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:53,400
It's as though the fate of the entire world is weighing down on it.

703
00:39:54,720 --> 00:39:56,230
I'm just a human.

704
00:39:56,850 --> 00:39:59,640
I've never once thought of becoming a deity that could save the world.

705
00:40:00,100 --> 00:40:02,140
But now, the world stands on the brink of catastrophe,

706
00:40:02,200 --> 00:40:04,480
its safety suddenly hanging by a thread.

707
00:40:05,160 --> 00:40:06,750
I cannot,

708
00:40:07,550 --> 00:40:08,870
and will not run away.

709
00:40:11,840 --> 00:40:13,130
Fan Yue.

710
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:16,610
Forgive me for leaving alone.

711
00:40:25,730 --> 00:40:27,110
Have you really thought it through?

712
00:40:27,720 --> 00:40:29,060
At this point,

713
00:40:29,270 --> 00:40:30,610
I have no choice.

714
00:40:30,630 --> 00:40:32,150
Fan Yue has almost expended himself

715
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:33,610
just to protect the Eternals and demons.

716
00:40:33,890 --> 00:40:35,800
I won't back down either.

717
00:40:35,900 --> 00:40:37,660
I have no idea if Fan Yue will ever wake up,

718
00:40:37,690 --> 00:40:38,690
or when that might be.

719
00:40:39,220 --> 00:40:41,010
But if he wakes up,

720
00:40:41,030 --> 00:40:42,940
you mustn't let him go to Cold Spring Palace.

721
00:40:44,740 --> 00:40:46,100
You may want to save the Eternals and demons,

722
00:40:46,120 --> 00:40:47,800
but have you ever thought about yourself?

723
00:40:48,360 --> 00:40:49,850
Mo Li is clearly targeting you

724
00:40:49,870 --> 00:40:51,270
by demanding you go alone.

725
00:40:55,190 --> 00:40:57,460
Back when my father was forced to die in Ning'an City,

726
00:40:57,900 --> 00:40:59,380
I hated the world

727
00:40:59,410 --> 00:41:01,490
when I was leaving.

728
00:41:01,510 --> 00:41:02,920
I didn't believe in Eternals,

729
00:41:02,940 --> 00:41:04,790
demons, humans,

730
00:41:04,820 --> 00:41:06,450
and even deities.

731
00:41:06,570 --> 00:41:08,400
But along the way,

732
00:41:08,440 --> 00:41:10,000
I found that among all races,

733
00:41:10,030 --> 00:41:11,800
there are still kindness.

734
00:41:11,830 --> 00:41:13,180
There are countless beings

735
00:41:13,200 --> 00:41:15,500
steadfastly upholding justice and their purpose.

736
00:41:15,610 --> 00:41:17,690
They shouldn't be destroyed this way,

737
00:41:17,710 --> 00:41:19,830
nor should the world end this way.

738
00:41:20,120 --> 00:41:21,960
But the Outlander King's Sword is already broken.

739
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:23,740
Even if you have the Divine Bow,

740
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:25,350
you don't have usable arrows.

741
00:41:25,370 --> 00:41:27,280
With just this trace of spiritual power left in you,

742
00:41:27,300 --> 00:41:28,620
your journey

743
00:41:29,390 --> 00:41:31,250
could very easily end in death.

744
00:41:31,410 --> 00:41:32,850
In this world,

745
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:34,740
it's not always about being certain of success

746
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:36,830
or guaranteeing that nothing will go wrong before we take action.

747
00:41:36,860 --> 00:41:38,930
Many times, we may not have the upper hand

748
00:41:38,950 --> 00:41:40,590
or any certainty of success,

749
00:41:40,610 --> 00:41:41,860
but we still risk it all

750
00:41:41,890 --> 00:41:43,480
to protect

751
00:41:43,510 --> 00:41:44,940
what matters to us,

752
00:41:44,990 --> 00:41:46,240
don't we?

753
00:41:47,040 --> 00:41:49,770
Everyone has their own responsibilities to fulfil.

754
00:41:49,790 --> 00:41:51,710
Though the physical form of deity Xing Yue may have perished,

755
00:41:51,740 --> 00:41:53,300
its Divine Mantle remains undiminished.

756
00:41:53,860 --> 00:41:56,180
Perhaps, it's also for this very purpose.

757
00:41:57,040 --> 00:41:57,870
Bai Shuo.

758
00:41:57,900 --> 00:41:58,630
Tian Huo.

759
00:41:59,740 --> 00:42:01,290
You've never feared death,

760
00:42:01,320 --> 00:42:02,690
whether it was for Fan Yue

761
00:42:02,710 --> 00:42:04,570
or Bright Moon Palace.

762
00:42:04,600 --> 00:42:06,920
You definitely would know

763
00:42:07,110 --> 00:42:09,110
and understand this feeling.

764
00:42:09,140 --> 00:42:09,970
Right?

765
00:42:12,990 --> 00:42:14,200
Don't worry.

766
00:42:14,220 --> 00:42:15,490
I cherish my life,

767
00:42:16,420 --> 00:42:18,740
and I generally have good luck.

768
00:42:18,880 --> 00:42:20,440
I won't die so easily.

769
00:42:35,510 --> 00:42:36,390
Tian Huo.

770
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:39,230
It has been my honor

771
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:40,980
to have known you

772
00:42:41,220 --> 00:42:42,630
and journeyed with you.

773
00:42:43,350 --> 00:42:44,760
Thank you

774
00:42:44,780 --> 00:42:46,130
for everything along the way.

775
00:42:46,990 --> 00:42:48,640
If I ever make it back,

776
00:42:49,090 --> 00:42:50,400
let's have a drink together.

777
00:43:04,580 --> 00:43:05,850
Bai Shuo is here.

778
00:43:06,900 --> 00:43:08,250
She really came.

779
00:43:10,200 --> 00:43:12,170
I didn't expect her to come.

780
00:43:22,770 --> 00:43:24,250
You really came.

781
00:43:25,240 --> 00:43:26,360
What?

782
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:28,320
Did Fan Yue not stop you?

783
00:43:28,350 --> 00:43:30,680
Or is he simply too weak to stop you?

784
00:43:30,970 --> 00:43:32,060
Let them go.

785
00:43:34,200 --> 00:43:37,280
Both the Eternals and demons have never been nice to you.

786
00:43:37,320 --> 00:43:38,650
They either look down on you

787
00:43:38,670 --> 00:43:40,190
or have been itching to fight or kill you.

788
00:43:40,220 --> 00:43:41,490
And yet, you still want to save them?

789
00:43:42,440 --> 00:43:44,400
There's no need for all this nonsense.

790
00:43:44,920 --> 00:43:46,520
You set the terms,

791
00:43:46,540 --> 00:43:48,180
and I showed up as agreed.

792
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:49,560
I have done what I needed to do.

793
00:43:50,070 --> 00:43:51,710
You should keep your promise too.

794
00:43:51,740 --> 00:43:52,700
Fine.

795
00:43:53,120 --> 00:43:55,430
As long as you promise me one thing,

796
00:43:55,450 --> 00:43:58,070
I will spare all of them.

797
00:43:58,140 --> 00:43:59,180
Bai Shuo.

798
00:43:59,300 --> 00:44:00,530
Don't believe him.

799
00:44:00,550 --> 00:44:01,650
Mo Li is ruthless.

800
00:44:01,680 --> 00:44:03,370
He won't give up so easily.

801
00:44:04,970 --> 00:44:06,030
How noisy.

802
00:44:09,820 --> 00:44:10,720
Where did they go?

803
00:44:10,740 --> 00:44:11,680
Don't worry.

804
00:44:11,700 --> 00:44:13,340
They went back to where they came from.

805
00:44:13,370 --> 00:44:15,210
Their lives are mine

806
00:44:15,230 --> 00:44:17,090
to take at any moment, anyway.

807
00:44:17,120 --> 00:44:18,680
What do you want me to do?

808
00:44:18,700 --> 00:44:20,960
The wedding that was left unfinished 60,000 years ago

809
00:44:21,960 --> 00:44:24,070
should now be completed.

810
00:44:24,220 --> 00:44:25,920
I'm not Xing Yue.

811
00:44:25,940 --> 00:44:26,860
It doesn't matter.

812
00:44:27,460 --> 00:44:28,710
I just want to finish

813
00:44:28,730 --> 00:44:30,820
what I didn't finish 60,000 years ago.

814
00:44:30,940 --> 00:44:33,120
So regardless whether you are Xing Yue or not,

815
00:44:33,150 --> 00:44:34,470
simply just with your face,

816
00:44:34,490 --> 00:44:36,340
I must marry you.
